text:
Request Pricing Information





  &lt;label for="fullName" class="form-label"&gt;Full Name*&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;input type="text" class="form-control" id="fullName" name="fullName" required&gt;
  &lt;div class="invalid-feedback"&gt;Please provide your full name.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
  &lt;label for="email" class="form-label"&gt;Business Email*&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" required&gt;
  &lt;div class="invalid-feedback"&gt;Please provide a valid email address.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
  &lt;label for="company" class="form-label"&gt;Company Name*&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;input type="text" class="form-control" id="company" name="company" required&gt;
  &lt;div class="invalid-feedback"&gt;Please provide your company name.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
  &lt;label for="phone" class="form-label"&gt;Phone Number&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;input type="tel" class="form-control" id="phone" name="phone"&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
  &lt;label for="jobTitle" class="form-label"&gt;Job Title*&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;input type="text" class="form-control" id="jobTitle" name="jobTitle" required&gt;
  &lt;div class="invalid-feedback"&gt;Please provide your job title.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
  &lt;label for="companySize" class="form-label"&gt;Company Size*&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;select class="form-select" id="companySize" name="companySize" required&gt;
    &lt;option value="" selected disabled&gt;Select company size&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="1-50"&gt;1-50 employees&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="51-200"&gt;51-200 employees&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="201-500"&gt;201-500 employees&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="501-1000"&gt;501-1000 employees&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="1001+"&gt;1001+ employees&lt;/option&gt;
  &lt;/select&gt;
  &lt;div class="invalid-feedback"&gt;Please select your company size.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
  &lt;label for="package" class="form-label"&gt;Package of Interest*&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;select class="form-select" id="package" name="package" required&gt;
    &lt;option value="" selected disabled&gt;Select package&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="Standard"&gt;Standard Package&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="Premium"&gt;Premium Package&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="Enterprise"&gt;Enterprise Solution&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="Implementation"&gt;Implementation Services&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="Unsure"&gt;Not sure yet&lt;/option&gt;
  &lt;/select&gt;
  &lt;div class="invalid-feedback"&gt;Please select a package.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
  &lt;label for="timeframe" class="form-label"&gt;Implementation Timeframe*&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;select class="form-select" id="timeframe" name="timeframe" required&gt;
    &lt;option value="" selected disabled&gt;Select timeframe&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="Immediate"&gt;Within 1 month&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="Soon"&gt;Within 3 months&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="Planning"&gt;Within 6 months&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="Exploring"&gt;Just exploring options&lt;/option&gt;
  &lt;/select&gt;
  &lt;div class="invalid-feedback"&gt;Please select your implementation timeframe.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-4"&gt;
  &lt;label for="requirements" class="form-label"&gt;Specific Requirements or Questions&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;textarea class="form-control" id="requirements" name="requirements" rows="4" placeholder="Please share any specific requirements, questions, or details about your compliance needs that would help us provide accurate pricing information."&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-3 form-check"&gt;
  &lt;input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" id="privacy" required&gt;
  &lt;label class="form-check-label" for="privacy"&gt;I agree to Kudoo's &lt;a href="privacy.qmd"&gt;Privacy Policy&lt;/a&gt;*&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;div class="invalid-feedback"&gt;You must agree to our Privacy Policy.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;button type="submit" class="cta-btn" style="width: 100%;"&gt;Request Pricing Information&lt;/button&gt;


:::
:::
:::
:::
This sales.qmd file includes:

A comprehensive overview of your sales approach and philosophy
Clear explanation of your sales process
Detailed information about different engagement models and packages
Industry specialization information
Leadership team profiles
Sales-related FAQs
Call-to-action sections
A pricing inquiry form section (which would require creating a forms/pricing.html file similar to your demo form)

The structure and styling match your existing pages while focusing specifically on the sales aspect of your business. You may need to adjust specific details like team member names, package details, and pricing models to match your actual offerings.
